  "prompt": "What are best computer games?",
  "response": "The \"best\" computer games can vary widely based on personal preferences, genres, and gaming styles. However, here are some highly acclaimed games across various genres that have made significant impacts in the gaming community:\n\n### Action/Adventure\n1. **The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt** - An expansive open-world RPG with a rich story and deep character development.\n2. **Red Dead Redemption 2** - A beautifully crafted story set in the American West with immersive gameplay and stunning visuals.\n\n### Role-Playing Games (RPG)\n3. **Persona 5 Royal** - A stylish JRPG that combines turn-based combat with social simulation elements.\n4. **Final Fantasy VII Remake** - A modern reimagining of the classic RPG with stunning graphics and an engaging battle system.\n\n### First-Person Shooters (FPS)\n5. **DOOM Eternal** - A fast-paced shooter with intense combat and a heavy metal soundtrack.\n6. **Valorant** - A tactical FPS that combines elements of hero shooters with traditional gunplay.\n\n### Strategy\n7. **Civilization VI** - A turn-based strategy game where you build and expand a civilization through different eras.\n8. **XCOM 2** - A tactical game that focuses on squad-based combat and strategic planning against alien forces.\n\n### Indie Games\n9. **Hades** - A roguelike dungeon crawler that combines fast-paced combat with a rich narrative and character development.\n10. **Celeste** - A platformer that features challenging gameplay and a touching story about mental health.\n\n### Simulation\n11. **Stardew Valley** - A farming simulation game that combines farming, crafting, and relationship-building in a charming pixel art world.\n12. **The Sims 4** - A life simulation game where you can create and control people, build homes, and navigate their lives.\n\n### Multiplayer/Co-op\n13. **Among Us** - A social deduction game that became a cultural phenomenon, focusing on teamwork and betrayal.\n14. **Minecraft** - A sandbox game that allows players to build, explore, and survive in a blocky 3D world.\n\n### Horror\n15. **Resident Evil Village** - A survival horror game that combines action and exploration with a gripping story.\n16. **Phasmophobia** - A co-op ghost-hunting game that blends horror and teamwork.\n\nThese games represent just a fraction of what's available, and the best choice for you will depend on your interests and gaming style. Always check reviews and gameplay videos to see what resonates with you!",
